originalText.text: Had my first root canal today and I was very happy with the whole experience. The women behind the desk in reception were so nice and professional even when a few people weren’t so patient. The whole team in the back were very kind and were very good about explaining what was happening. For the procedure itself I could tell that my dentist had plenty of experience and I felt very little. She made sure I wasn’t in pain and I would say the procedure took about 25 - 30 mins total and I was on my way. I would recommend them 100%.

originalText.text: Im not a big review guy but i felt the need to give this place a big hit!  I needed a root canal and went there on emergency.  They were so so quick, professional and  kind.  First rate modern equipment.  I inly wish my dentist at home had this operation! But its nyc you better be amazing and they are!!!

originalText.text: crowded, chaotic office.  Staff climbing over each other to process patients, it feels like a dental exam on a subway platform at rush hour.  A question I asked the dental tech regarding previous x-rays was ignored, she just mumbled something unintelligible behind her mask and kept working. this dentist was a recommended referral so I am hoping that the final procedure outcome will surpass (and make me forget) the initial exam.

originalText.text:
This visit for a root canal went extremely smoothly.  The appointment started on time, they did their own evaluation to confirm what my dentist thought was the problem, and then started the procedure immediately.  I felt
no pain at all and was updated throughout the entire experience.  I hope to never need another root canal, but if so, I would absolutely return here.

originalText.text:
It was a pleasure indeed to be seen by Dr. Kamen Genov at MHE!
Anticipating a root-canal treatment is never a pleasant emotion, pain expectation, etc.
However, nothing further from this occurred; pleasant environment, gentle care and NO pain whatsoever!
I would highly recommend MHE to anyone in need of a root-canal treatment.
